xternal text\" href=\"//dx.doi.org/10.1007%2Fs10902-009-9136-7\">10.1007/s10902-009-9136-7</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-05-22</span></span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARuut+Veenhoven&amp;rft.atitle=An+Entertaining+Travelogue&amp;rft.au=Chekola%2C+Mark&amp;rft.aufirst=Mark&amp;rft.aulast=Chekola&amp;rft.date=2009-10-01&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%252Fs10902-009-9136-7%3FLI%3Dtrue&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1007%2Fs10902-009-9136-7&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Happiness+Studies&amp;rft.pages=631-633&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=10\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Frisch-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Frisch_3-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation web\">Frisch, Michael. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://bearspace.baylor.edu/Michael_B_Frisch/www/oral-histories.html\">\"Proofessor\"</a>. <i>The meaningful life project</i>. Frisch, Michael B. (2008). The Oral History and Education Project of the International Society for Quality of Life Studies and the Gallup Institute for Global Well Being: A Way to Honor Distinguished Researchers and to Preserve their Legacies. Applied Research in Quality of Life, 2 (4), 223-238<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-05-22</span></span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARuut+Veenhoven&amp;rft.atitle=Proofessor&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rft.au=Frisch%2C+Michael&amp;rft.aulast=Frisch&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbearspace.baylor.edu%2FMichael_B_Frisch%2Fwww%2Foral-histories.html&amp;rft.jtitle=The+meaningful+life+project&amp;rft.pub=Frisch%2C+Michael+B.+%282008%2